Title: The Contest
Plot: Andy and Adriana start planning for a future worthy of a first family.  Louis preps for the "Funniest Celebrity in Washington" contest, while his opponent, Penn Jillette, preps for their senate race.  Back at the house, the Watt brothers find a new way to taunt Gil John.
